    <main id="main-content">
        <!-- Hero Section -->
        <section class="issue-hero" style="background-image: url('assets/images/placeholder-hero.jpg');">
            <div class="issue-hero-overlay"></div>
            <div class="container">
                <div class="issue-hero-content">
                    <h1>Housing as a Human Right & Chosen Family Homes</h1>
                    <p class="issue-hero-description">Guaranteeing housing for all trans people, especially those rejected by families - through haus collectives, community land trusts, and abolishing landlord exploitation.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Overview Section -->
        <section class="issue-overview-section">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="issue-overview-content">
                    <h2>Overview</h2>
                    <p>Housing is a human right, not a commodity for landlords to profit from. Trans women face staggering rates of homelessness - especially trans youth rejected by biological families and sex workers denied housing due to criminalization. We demand housing for ALL, prioritizing those most vulnerable: trans women of color, sex workers, disabled folks, and anyone rejected by blood family.</p>
                    <p>We're building haus collective housing where chosen families can live together with legal recognition, community land trusts that remove housing from the speculative market, and anti-gentrification protections that keep QTPOC neighborhoods from being displaced by wealthy developers. Housing should not require proving "worthiness" to landlords or submitting to surveillance.</p>
                    <p>Through mutual aid housing networks, rent strikes against exploitative landlords, and guaranteed housing programs, we're ensuring every trans person has a safe place to call home - whether in a haus with chosen family or independently, without discrimination based on gender identity, sex work, or income.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Key Initiatives -->
        <section class="initiatives-section">
            <div class="container">
                <h2>Key Initiatives</h2>
                <div class="initiatives-grid">
                    <div class="initiative-card">
                        <span class="initiative-icon">✨</span>
                        <h3>Trans Housing Guarantee</h3>
                        <p>Guaranteed housing for all trans people, especially those rejected by families. No questions asked, no "proving worthiness" to landlords, no discrimination.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="initiative-card">
                        <span class="initiative-icon">🏠</span>
                        <h3>Haus Collective Housing</h3>
                        <p>Legal recognition and funding for ballroom-style haus collective housing where chosen families live together with shared resources and mutual support.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="initiative-card">
                        <span class="initiative-icon">🛡️</span>
                        <h3>Sex Worker Housing Rights</h3>
                        <p>End housing discrimination against sex workers. No evictions or denials based on profession. Sex work is work and deserves housing security.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="initiative-card">
                        <span class="initiative-icon">🌍</span>
                        <h3>Community Land Trusts</h3>
                        <p>Removing housing from speculative markets through community land trusts. QTPOC neighborhoods stay QTPOC, not gentrified by wealthy developers.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="initiative-card">
                        <span class="initiative-icon">⚖️</span>
                        <h3>Rent Strike Support</h3>
                        <p>Legal defense and mutual aid for tenants organizing rent strikes against exploitative landlords. Abolish landlordism, guarantee housing for all.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="initiative-card">
                        <span class="initiative-icon">🏳️‍⚧️</span>
                        <h3>Trans Youth Safe Housing</h3>
                        <p>Emergency and permanent housing for trans youth rejected by biological families, with haus placement and chosen family support structures.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

